node.text:
Puck was bouncin on me hard today guys my apologies, I wanted to get this clip out a little cleaner😅 

I wanna see what skills you guys have! If you have any hockey videos uploaded please drop a comment below, gonna be reacting to videos next week 🙏🙏😎

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Zac Bell in Rogers Headquarters with @shawnmckenzie89. May be an image of 2 people, people sitting, people standing, wrist watch and indoor.

node.text: Had a blast on the show today w Shawner big thanks for havin me out 🔥
